      • isDisplayOldToNew

        public boolean isDisplayOldToNew()
        Returns the order in which the log is displayed.

        If true, older log messages are displayed at the top of the log, newer messages at the bottom. If false, newer messages are on top, older messages at the bottom.

        Returns:
        whether the log is displayed in old-to-new order
        See Also:
        setDisplayOldToNew(boolean)
